console 下交换键位
#1.复制/usr/share/keymaps/i386/qwerty/us.map.gz 到Swap_Cap_Ctl.map.gz
#2.解压Swap_Cap_Ctl.map.gz,修改其中的Caps_lock 和 Control对应的keycodes
#3.压缩Swap_Cap_Ctl.map 
#4.修改/etc/vconsole.conf 改为KEYMAP=Swap_Cap_Ctl
1. 修改/etc/vconsole.conf 改为KEYMAP=emacs

X 下交换键位
添加以下内容到/etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/00-keyboard.conf
# Read and parsed by systemd-localed. It's probably wise not to edit this file
# manually too freely.
Section "InputClass"
	Identifier "system-keyboard"
	MatchIsKeyboard "on"
	Option "XkbLayout" "us"
	Option "XkbOptions" "ctrl:swapcaps"
EndSection


然后reboot
